OL,3,C'We failed our colleagues,' but I was
OL,4,Cnot aware of abuse, says Harrods boss
OL,6,FMr Ward, who has been at Harrods since
OL,7,F2006, and worked for Fayed until the
OL,8,Fchange of ownership in 2010, said an
OL,9,Findependent review was underway into
OL,10,Fissues arising from the allegations.
OL,12,FHe said he had provided information to
OL,13,Fensure his conduct could be reviewed.
OL,15,FHis statement said: "While it is true
OL,16,Fthat rumours of his behaviour
OL,17,Fcirculated in the public domain, no
OL,18,Fcharges or allegations were ever put
OL,19,Fto me by the police, the CPS, internal
OL,20,Fchannels or others.
